<subSubSection id="144337CEF165851A9C3D8B89D709FC6D" pageId="null" pageNumber="114" type="description">
<paragraph id="3C484F97032A0862348257DABD6CE508" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">
Unterscheidet sich von 
<taxonomicName id="7B17988F10968150192AB9B19FF28A08" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Papaveraceae" genus="Papaver" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="114" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="105E564C6AC8FFF4C086EE16FED43A70" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">Papaver</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
(S. 108) durch folgende Merkmale: 
<emphasis id="042BEAD92DA8EF9B62C7DE340024171E" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">Milchsaft gelb; Narbenstrahlen 4-8, von der Spitze eines kurzen Griffels herablaufend.</emphasis>
</paragraph>
<paragraph id="E42D616A0B9C8161D0394672B75D12FF" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">
Die Gattung 
<taxonomicName id="3CA631D2842C4737EF5445BB2B42FCE6" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Papaveraceae" genus="Meconopsis" kingdom="Plantae" order="Ranunculales" pageId="null" pageNumber="114" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="genus">
<emphasis id="390D6B3BECA673D4E3138BD0B6AA9C9F" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">Meconopsis</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
<normalizedToken id="AB7DE723D6E79037A179B38D9A0DCD00" originalValue="umfaßt" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">umfasst</normalizedToken>
etwa 
<emphasis id="B5629FA6EFCE1BB831323476B4F02524" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">30 Arten</emphasis>
und ist vorwiegend in 
<emphasis id="6F0CC687641A77D5DCAEBD0167833306" italics="true" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">Zentralasien</emphasis>
verbreitet. 
<normalizedToken id="3713C4923794B5276839B56C8E188222" originalValue="Über" pageId="null" pageNumber="114">Ueber</normalizedToken>
Morphologie vgl. Taylor (1934).
</paragraph>
</subSubSection>
